      "span_text": "In a proteomic study, the alterations in protein expression of human dendritic cells, treated with 0.1% alcohol for 24 h, were investigated by 2D gel electrophoresis followed by liquid chromotgraphy (LC)-MS and confirmed at the gene expression level by qRT-PCR."
